{"tid":1747480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"只要做到呢樣野 聽日區選香港人一定會贏","createTime":"2019-11-23T08:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T18:33:54.000Z","uid":297439,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fdb3d72f1d04ee933285c61ce896d1fc4596b9","tid":1747480,"uid":297439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"大家都知道<br />\n保皇嘅票絕大多數都係來自掌心雷種票<br />\n絕大多數老人家根本連自己做緊乜都唔知就俾建制派呃去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇返數據<br />\n老年選民比例本身已經佔最大部分 重要極高投票率<br />\n可見掌心雷嘅規模係極大<br />\n而呢個代表<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>就算民望幾低保皇黨都可以靠掌心雷贏</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n聽日區議會選舉要贏嘅話<br />\n剩係自己去投票係絕對唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全香港人聽日朝早<br />\n返去搵自己嘅爺爺嫲嫲公公婆婆飲茶</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再去投票<br />\n冇哂掌心雷班垃圾保皇黨根本就冇可能贏<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再俾長者繼續淪為保皇黨嘅種票工具<br />\n踢走嗰班卑鄙賣港嘅保皇黨出議會</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/14446/1*TZvFUxGt7n8T3XNm4j-90w.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F14446%2F1%2ATZvFUxGt7n8T3XNm4j-90w.jpeg&h=e23c26ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5604b1d7169ae5dbbd08c93d8dd0be5dced0c70a","tid":1747480,"uid":297439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:40:26.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬當年贏嘅其中一個原因<br />\n就係年青支持者搵返自己爺爺嫲嫲投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35a2b4a5b4b403e9da4a06298225822cc2909ec","tid":1747480,"uid":297439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"政府公然縱容掌心雷 教票站職員唔好理佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9OEnnMveQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT9OEnnMveQg&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=18e90a4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9OEnnMveQg</a><br />\n<br />\n垃圾政府唔做 香港人自己做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0eab40906e61fa61f333cb12d1023197b420e8a","tid":1747480,"uid":59700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"射落海果班都係鬼"},{"pid":"638a948ab26802b3367601dc6e769d2ffcc7e2c6","tid":1747480,"uid":34955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0eab40906e61fa61f333cb12d1023197b420e8a","tid":1747480,"uid":59700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"射落海果班都係鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:45:38.000Z","msg":"3年前嘅招數依家重諗住攞黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8704d07d5fa44534e2b23991ff8e104d466b466c","tid":1747480,"uid":297439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608462d7c520e53f0c3ac90ee2074ed7f1772712","tid":1747480,"uid":255092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:05:50.000Z","msg":"幫佢地保管好身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb01359100191fe49dcc399f2adae9a847a9a6b","tid":1747480,"uid":297439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:09:32.000Z","msg":"繼續俾掌心雷凌駕自己嘅選票<br />\n香港人你甘心咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" 